Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:07.00,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}發信者：露易絲·哈勒維\N到達表兄弟家了\N大家很久沒見到了，都大大的\N變化了呢，嚇了一跳\N覺得我不在大家都很寂寞呢\N不要做奇怪的事情喲(笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:10.13,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}表兄弟家是由古老的城堡改造而來的\N雖說是中庭，但也相當寬闊\N聽說連料理也由專門僱傭的廚師來做\N真期待明天的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事 左手的再生治療竟然無法實施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創部的干細胞發現有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據醫生說明 Gundam的Beam武器可能引起了細胞再生障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.17,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}早上好\N昨天的理科課\N有些地方不是很明白\N(不會是睡著了吧？沒睡著的吧？)\N今天上課前來問你\N拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.83,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往桑坦德機場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:59.39,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}發信者：露易絲·哈勒維\N主題：致沙慈\N謝謝你來看我\N已經上飛機了嗎？\N不會還留在西班牙吧\N你已經缺席不少課了\N可要趕快回去上喲\N代我問你姐姐好\N沙慈的夢想是我們兩個人的夢想\N請一定要努力學習\N\N在宇宙等著我\N我一定會追上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 沙慈 一定要聽話乖乖回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙等著我 我一定會追上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:55.34,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}美國 國聯議會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對天行者組織反覆引發的窮凶極惡的恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION 人類革新聯盟 AEU 將建立軍事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣佈 我們將在國聯管理之下 為殲滅天行者組織而採取軍事行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個陣營在國聯的管理下發表了軍事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此誕生了史上最龐大的國聯軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來事態隨著天行者組織的預想在發展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近採取的過激武力介入 是為了國聯軍隊的統一而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想挺妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界團結為一 這是天行者組織的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用戰鬥來否定戰鬥 贏得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你所追求的世界嗎 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於完成了計劃的第一階段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然誘因是三位一體的行動 這一點讓我感到有些荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有些不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國的軍事基地由於三位一體的襲擊而受到重創
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的情況下 就算統一軍隊也得不到什麼結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會引起輿論的失望與反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼內情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我感到有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔資料中沒有記載三位一體的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且維塔遭受了資料篡改 這一點不得不使我感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡發來的暗號通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師與機體一起返回托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 作戰會議 要回宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察國聯軍隊的動向之後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的實力 應該已經預測到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 先要做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊昂先生 麻煩你帶上拉塞去收取GN兵裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵裝終於投入運作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也就一架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘下的成員開始登艦Gundam的回收工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵裝終於投入戰鬥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們面臨著不得不這樣做的處境
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:37.97,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Union 美國 伊利諾斯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐 從新型Gundam手裡搶到的Beam Sabel的調查結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像天行者組織裡出現了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:06:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且作為見面禮 把和Gundam同類型的引擎以及搭載該引擎的MS提供給了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有30架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能做出那樣的聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些機體的駕駛員 應該將從Over Flag隊員中選取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 也就是隊長你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將用Flag擊倒Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在霍華德·梅森的墓前發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 隊長 依靠Flag的性能 對Gundam有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫一言既出 駟馬難追
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:43.82,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革聯 俄羅斯南部 軍事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 Gundam的主要器官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據資料 正式名稱似乎是GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人革聯分配到的GN Drive有十部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師的人選就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 請讓我擔任新型機的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要給我擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說少尉放出的腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠對長翅膀的Gundam的機師產生影響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一優勢 不能不利用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候別給我掉鏈子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:36.94,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}AEU 法國 基地內士官宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師候補 只要集合AEU所屬國的精英就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要不要算上那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特利庫·克拉薩瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 邀請大佐共進晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 現在世界正迎來巨大的變革時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這一點你什麼都沒有考慮過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是 不能扔著不管的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 我準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:25.85,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}軌道列車公司 會長別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是JNN麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去告訴他們與此有關的 一概不予回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受歡迎也真是不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 機體的搬送正在順利進行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我完成貸款份額的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那·哈維總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請容我單刀直入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬送中新型機 請讓給我一架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼UNION也好AEU也好都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請以總裁的權限 安排我進入軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本是所屬外國部隊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱作加裡·比亞吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的技術之高明我是聽說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不惜至此而想駕駛那個的理由是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個三次到嘴邊卻放跑了的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…雖然也有這個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感覺中不遠的將來不再需要傭兵的時代就會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少 想要去能夠戰鬥的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底知道了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了只是感覺而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排就拜託您了哦 總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽的 全因為天行什麼的玩意兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取材撲了個空 怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 說是總裁在跟人見面中…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麼事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是JNN的特派員 有些事情想問大哥一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JNN的記者小姐啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不介意 但我稍微有點急事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在車上談的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絹江·庫洛斯洛特小姐是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 要是像你這樣美麗的記者小姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 想要問我的事情是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果錯了的話我表示道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比亞吉先生剛才和列車公司的總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那·哈維先生見面了對麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都談了些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我談了些流通業的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認物資流通狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來向總裁報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意來向總裁…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是私事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 私事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不冒犯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告知我那些物資是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…GN Drive…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道列車相關的器材什麼的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是驅動MS的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…MS的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織所擁有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個庫爾吉斯的少年兵作為機師的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯的…少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架 洗腦 讓他接受戰鬥訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為游擊隊士兵的 不瞞你說 就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭狂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法抑制的喜愛戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循人類原始的衝動生活 是最差勁最惡劣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐還在出差麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人的老鼠已經清理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是認為這是獲得輿論支持最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狡猾的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸…   沙…沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:43.77,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}UNION 高軌道空間站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下認為 亞里桑德羅大人沒有特地同行的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你費盡千辛萬苦才得到的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我親眼見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這可是科納一族長久以來的夙願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里桑德羅大人 不 應該說科納家\N早在數代之前就已經策劃對計劃進行干涉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 由於維塔的存在 我們什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候一次偶然 天使降臨在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你 裡本斯·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了報答您把我撿回來的恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 竟然能找到本體的所在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了這麼長時間 實在很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯 你就是我的天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:44.98,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲大陸 西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前這麼努力工作 突然間失去聯絡 搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我啊 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮複雜的問題我不拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇哥確實是這種類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 找剁麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾 哈羅是三位一體不可缺少的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 剛才是開玩笑 開玩笑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那傳來了任務計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容和往常一樣 作戰於3天後進行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 如何突破的安全系統
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的 怎麼說也到了這裡 怎麼能隨便放她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的女士 印象中在維塔的資料裡看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給您留下印象是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天行者的情報員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是我的搭檔 紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是個好男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到達這裡 你們的能力之高我瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 找我們有什麼事麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來打聲招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體組也和我們一樣是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為情報員的我們對你們提供支持也是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是受到了那邊Gundam的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事情我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我並不是那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 持中立立場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只是遵循伊奧利亞·肖漢博格的理念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外沒有任何立場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 王留美 需要的時候我們會期待你的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方不要告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 大哥 讓他們就這樣回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 而且手裡能打得牌多一張也是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是美女 只要是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別歪曲 別歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 大小姐 天行者正和他們處於敵對狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 因為三位一體正在誘發世界的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那麼討厭現在的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我覺得如果世界不改變的話 毀滅了也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒什麼變化 三位一體也沒有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我違反了命令 甘願受罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過這事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪 三位一體開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 他們的攻擊目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們行進路線上的軍事基地是人革聯廣州軍區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:21.72,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}人革聯 廣州方面軍屯駐基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測班通知全員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似三台新型Gundam的MS影像從S9788方向襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計將會對本基地進行軍事介入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的怨氣我一直留到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我徹底發洩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作戰時就沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等你這話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了一台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害怕 集中火力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面打 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜魚 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這些魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以到我肩上來了 準備合體攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Exia嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有10架組成的編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們也放出了GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些又是天行者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超部Jinx部隊 開始攻擊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎之子的10架 決不能讓對方擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼機動性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎樣的性能阿 果然這個機體 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連Gundam什麼的 也快不足畏懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體能夠趕上我的反應速度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢打壞我的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看下面的基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 為什麼 明明遭到了那樣的重創
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉還是第一次嘗到吧 這就是所謂勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體脫離了戰鬥空域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們遇到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革聯投入了載有太陽爐的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 維塔的情報洩露了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後就是Gundam之間的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣世界也正在變化 變化的盡頭究竟會是怎樣的未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡了 亞里桑德羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是維塔 伊奧利亞·肖漢博格 不 是構成天行者的根基的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對抗Gundam的新型MS磨刀霍霍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對根絕戰爭這一夢想的追求者的定罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 毀滅之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是世界的答案



